description:
Job Descriptions


Follow through the entire merchandising process from Yardage & Trims sourcing, product development, sampling, bulk production to delivery;
Regular meeting with sales team to identify customer’s needs;
Closely liaise with design team in product development stage and provide professional advices to improve cost efficiency and to better meet customer’s needs;
Prepare purchase orders and monitor the overall production schedule;
Communicate and coordinate with vendors, suppliers and manufacturers to ensure bulk quality and on-time delivery;
Look for new suppliers to cope with company’s development;
Frequently review cost sheets and conduct price negotiations with various parties;
Ensure data accuracy and maintain records in system.
Ad-hoc projects upon assignment.

Requirements


Diploma or above in Fashion, Clothing, Textile, Merchandising or other related disciplines;
5 years of solid experience;
Strong product knowledge of garment and other fashion accessories;
Proficiency in MS office;
Detail-minded, independent and able to meet tight schedule;
Strong negotiation, communication and problem-solving skills;
Good command of written and spoken English, Mandarin and Cantonese;
Willing to travel to PRC 
Interested candidates, please send your full resume with expected salary to us for interview.
